     6→ * This stage runs ONLY for AI-classified emails and is responsible for:
     7→ * - Filtering secondary labels based on relative confidence thresholds
     8→ * - Enforcing allowed category combinations (e.g., prevent "Shopping" + "Work")
     9→ * - Limiting to maxLabels configuration
    10→ * - Assigning final primary and secondary category labels
    11→ * - Generating label filtering rationale for explainability
